{
  "id": "adv_main_02_02_04",
  "title": "東京編1章9話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さん達が、いきなり私達と\nダンスを合わせる……ってことですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean you want to just jump in\nand dance alongside us‚ Rui-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ですがみなさんは、私達の全体曲の歌とダンスを\n覚えているんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But do you all have all our songs and dances\nmemorized?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.966666666666663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。ライバルの研究は\n日頃から念入りに行っているので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We do. We study our rivals\nseriously every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.866666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、パート分けもバッチリやで？\nレッスンの休憩中に、よく歌って踊ってるからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve even perfectly divided up the roles as well.\nWe often sing and dance to your songs during our lesson breaks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.433333333333326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "休憩中なのに……？　凄い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During your breaks? Wow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.843409718924416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "それに、せっかく同じ事務所へ所属になったんだし\nバラバラで練習するのは寂しいじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ since we’re all at the same agency now‚\nit’d be lonely if we practiced separately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.764724943889828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……などと、軽い気持ちで始めたら……）\n（とんでもないことになったな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It started casually like this. But then…）\n（…it blew way out of proportion.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 32033.33333333334,
          "startTime": 69.96666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33666.666666666664,
          "startTime": 71.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 40.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "嘘……でしょ？\nいくら振り付けも曲も覚えているからって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way…\nHow is that possible? Even if they did practice our dance moves and our songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……それぞれのパートと立ち位置……\n移動まで……全部、完璧だったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* They knew all our parts and positions…\neven the formation changes… It was all perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "それに……悔しいけど、私よりも全然……うまい\n今、初めて合わせたばかりのはずなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… I hate to admit it‚ but they’re all… much better than us.\nEven though this was their first time dancing in step with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……どうだったかしら？\n気持ち、走り過ぎていた気もするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How did we do?\nDid we get a little ahead of ourselves?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、ないです。むしろ\nビックリしちゃって、こっちが遅れちゃったぐらい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no‚ not at all. If anything‚\nwe’re so shocked that we feel left in the dust.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（トリエルの三人は息一つ切らせていない）\n（ペースが乱れたさくら達は仕方ないとしても……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（TRINITYAiLE isn’t at all out of breath.）\n（I can’t blame Sakura and the others for feeling disoriented‚ but still…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも私も\n初めて合わせてみて、勉強になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I learned a lot‚ too‚\nfrom dancing with you guys for the first time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "思っていた通り……まだまだうちらは、うまくなれる\nBIG4にも、勝てるぐらいに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as I thought‚ we still have a long way to grow\nuntil we can beat the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4……VENUSプログラム上位に君臨する\nアイドル達……だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "BIG4… Those are the idols who reign\nat the top of the VENUS Program‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはもう、そこまで見据えてるんだ……\nなのに、私達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ you guys already have your sights set that high.\nMeanwhile‚ look at us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "新人のグランプリで一回優勝しただけで\n少し舞い上がっていたのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we got a little complacent just because we\nwon the newcomer Grand Prix once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなことないと思うわ。一緒に踊ってみて\n感じたもの。前よりも、動きにキレが出ていたって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be so hard on yourselves. When dancing with you girls‚\nI felt something. Your moves were sharper than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "けどもし、そう言われても自分達では納得できなくて\n舞い上がっていたって思うんだったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if hearing that from me still makes you doubt yourselves‚\nand you feel like you got complacent from your victory…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 134.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "納得出来るまで、練習を重ねるしかない\n……そういうことですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then we’ll just have to keep practicing until we’re satisfied.\nIs that what you wanted to say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "確かにトリエルのダンスは凄かったけど\n圧倒されたままじゃ終われないもんね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your dancing was amazing‚ TRINITYAiLE‚\nbut we’re not gonna sit around letting it overwhelm us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "踊ろう\n今よりもっと上手になって……輝くために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s dance.\nLet’s get even better than before… so we can shine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "うん！\n目指すはトップアイドルだもん。がんばろー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup!\nWe’re aiming to be top idols‚ after all. Let’s do this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 155.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 158.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、改めて\n瑠依さん、優さん、すみれさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ once again‚\nRui-san‚ Yu-san‚ Sumire-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "星見プロダクションへようこそ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome to Hoshimi Productions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか変な感じだよね～\nトリエルが芽衣達と同じ事務所に入るなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This feels kinda strange.\nHaving TRINITYAiLE at the same agency as us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリで優勝を争った三グループだもんね……\n確かに不思議な縁よねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ all three of our groups did compete for the Grand Prix title.\nWe definitely have a strange connection.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
