      "text": "東京に来てから、こうやってみんなでわいわいする\n機会、減っちゃったから……今日は嬉しいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since we moved to Tokyo‚ I’ve had fewer opportunities\nto hang out with the girls like this… so I really appreciate today.",
